# VapeChoice — Premium Vape E-Commerce Website

A cinematic, scroll-driven vape storefront with galaxy theming, GSAP-powered animations, and a fully responsive design.

## Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **Next.js 14** (App Router) | Framework, SSR, routing, SEO |
| **Tailwind CSS v3** | Utility-first styling |
| **GSAP + ScrollTrigger** | Scroll-pinned animations, card stacks, bento morph |
| **Framer Motion** | Micro-interactions (hover, fade, scale) |
| **Google Fonts** | Poppins (headings) + Inter (body) |

## Design System (Galaxy Theme)

| Token | Value |
|---|---|
| BG Gradient | `#0f0c29 → #302b63 → #24243e` |
| Neon Purple | `#a855f7` |
| Electric Blue | `#3b82f6` |
| White | `#ffffff` |
| Sand | `#d6c6b8` |
| Rock Grey | `#2e2e2e` |
| Heading Font | Poppins / Space Grotesk |
| Body Font | Inter |

