### 2. Layout & Global Styles

#### [NEW] `app/layout.tsx`
- Root layout with Google Fonts (Poppins + Inter)
- Galaxy gradient background on `<body>`
- Smooth scroll behavior
- Global navbar (sticky, glassmorphism)

#### [NEW] `app/globals.css`
- Tailwind directives + custom CSS variables for galaxy palette
- Neon glow utilities (box-shadow, text-shadow)
- Scrollbar styling (dark theme)
