### 3. Components (8 Sections)

#### [NEW] `components/Navbar.tsx`
- Sticky glassmorphism header
- Logo (from `images/logo image.png`)
- Nav links: Home, Shop, Collections, Contact
- Mobile hamburger menu with slide-in drawer
- Scroll-triggered background opacity

#### [NEW] `components/HeroSection.tsx` — Section 1: Cinematic Hero
- **Reference**: [GSAP Scrubbed Bento Gallery](https://demos.gsap.com/demo/scrubbed-bento-gallery/)
- Full-viewport pinned section
- Large vape product image as center focus (using Aspire/Uwell product image)
- GSAP ScrollTrigger: pin + scrub animation
- Product scales from 1 → 1.1 with floating motion
- Text reveals from right on scroll: *"Choose Your Flavor. Own Your Vibe."*
- Subtext: *"Premium Vapes, Pods & Accessories"*
- CTA button: "Shop Now" with neon glow
- Smoke/particle effect via CSS gradients

#### [NEW] `components/OverlayScrollSections.tsx` — Section 2: Category Story Panels
- **Reference**: [GSAP Pinned Panels with Overscroll](https://demos.gsap.com/demo/pinned-panels-with-overscroll/)
- 4 full-screen sticky panels: **Vapes**, **Pods**, **E-Liquids**, **Accessories**
- Each panel is pinned; next slides over previous
- Previous panel scales down (0.95) + blurs
- Image-dominant with minimal text overlay
- Uses representative product images from each category folder

#### [NEW] `components/BestSellers.tsx` — Section 3: Card Stack
- **Reference**: [GSAP Card Stack](https://demos.gsap.com/demo/card-stack/)
- Section title: "Best Sellers" (centered)
- Cards stacked vertically, pinned during scroll
- Active card comes forward; previous fades/zooms back
- Card content: Product Image, Name, Price, "Add to Cart" button
- Active card gets neon purple glow effect
- Z-index stacking for depth illusion
- 6 best-seller products from across categories

#### [NEW] `components/DiscountSection.tsx` — Section 4: Sale Zone
- Dark galaxy background with extra depth
- Neon purple + blue accent stripes
- Grid layout of discounted products (4-6 cards)
- Pulsing animated discount badge (% OFF)
- Optional countdown timer
- Hover glow effect on cards
- Responsive: 1 col mobile → 2 col tablet → 3-4 col desktop

#### [NEW] `components/OurStory.tsx` — Section 5: Brand Story
- Minimal + emotional + premium feel
- Split layout: Left image (lifestyle), Right text
- Story text: *"VapeChoice was built for those who don't follow trends — they create them..."*
- Fade-in on scroll with soft slide-up (Framer Motion)
- Responsive: stacks vertically on mobile

#### [NEW] `components/ShopByCollection.tsx` — Section 6: Infinite Card Slider
- **Reference**: [GSAP Infinite Card Slider](https://demos.gsap.com/demo/infinite-card-slider/)
- Section title: "Shop by Collection"
- Infinite horizontal scrolling cards (GSAP seamless loop)
- Categories: Vapes, Pods, E-liquids, Accessories, Disposable Vapes
- Rounded glass cards with image + category name overlay
- Hover: slow animation + scale up + glow
- Click: navigates to category
- Drag support for mobile

#### [NEW] `components/BrandCarousel.tsx` — Section 7: Shop by Brand
- Circular logo carousel with auto infinite scroll
- Brands: SMOK, Voopoo, Vaporesso (text-based logos with neon styling)
- Hover: scale + glow effect
- Smooth continuous horizontal motion

#### [NEW] `components/Footer.tsx` — Section 8: Footer
- Dark footer with galaxy gradient continuation
- Logo + tagline
- Quick links column
- Categories column
- Contact info column
- Social media icons (Instagram, Twitter, Facebook)
- Responsive grid layout

