## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Product Data**: The layout references products with names and prices. I'll use realistic placeholder names/prices based on the image filenames (e.g., "Aspire Minican Plus" at AED 89). Should I use specific pricing you have in mind?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Currency**: I'll default to **AED** (based on your existing Shopify store pattern). Please confirm if this is correct.

> [!WARNING]
> **Images**: Some product images are small (360px). They'll be used at their native resolution. For the hero section and full-screen panels, I'll use CSS techniques (object-fit, backdrop-blur) to make them work at large scales without looking pixelated.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Brand Logos**: You mentioned SMOK, Voopoo, Vaporesso. I don't have logo images for these brands — I'll create stylized text-based logos with neon effects. If you have actual logo files, please provide them.

## Open Questions

1. **Pricing**: What prices should products display? (I'll use realistic defaults if not specified)
2. **Navigation**: Should the navbar have a cart icon / wishlist icon?
3. **Age Gate**: Many vape sites require an age verification popup — do you want one?

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` to verify no build errors
- Run `npm run dev` and verify all sections render

### Manual Verification
- Browser test at multiple breakpoints (320px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px)
- Verify all GSAP scroll animations trigger correctly
- Verify all images load from the `public/images/` directory
- Test mobile hamburger menu functionality
- Record a browser walkthrough video of the complete scroll experience
